lead_paragraph: The greatest achievement in Iceland's soccer history came easier than expected as a lacklustre England failed to put the tournament debutantes under any serious pressure, coach Hallgrimsson said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Iceland's Greatest Win Easier Than Expected, Says Coach
